{"tid":2177526,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李怡: 重挑721的意義","createTime":"2020-08-27T19:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T19:32:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99bf30a3ea7de706405df6bbabb7475fe756ca42","tid":2177526,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T19:06:08.000Z","msg":"連登討論區設題「恭喜香港警察令國際重溫煲大721事件」，留言刊登國際媒體關於港警指鹿為馬的報道連結，各社交媒體也紛紛重刊去年721以來的所有影片：現場直播，其後的綜合報道，包括播出五個多月就有832萬瀏覽的《721元朗黑夜》，和上月播出有130多萬瀏覽的《721誰主真相》。社交媒體出現大量影視真相挑戰謊言的民間行動大爆發。<br />\n<br />\n重挑721的意義，可從這兩段話中找尋。<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼明明知道我們知道他們在說謊，而仍然要說謊呢？因為在極權支配的暴政下，揑造謊言不是要人民相信，而是要向上級交代的自圓其說。721是整個反送中過程中，扭轉香港市民和國際社會對港警和政府觀感的關鍵事件，也就是說，此事件後，香港警察已從保護市民的形象一下子淪為暴政的工具。因此，指鹿為馬不是要市民相信，而是要「自己人」包括上級「假裝相信」，這樣才能夠維持「假裝正當性」。<br />\n<br />\n重新挑起這事件的另一意義，就是從這種明知騙不了人而仍然要說謊的行為，證明了現有的政權已是如假包換的暴政。<br />\n<br />\n索忍尼辛說，「暴政在虛假中找到了它唯一的避難所，虛假在暴政中找到了它唯一的支持。」「暴政必然與虛假交織在一起，它們之間有着最親密的、最深刻的自然結合。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/VAU3DHOLUJAMPFA7HC37RJKB6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2FVAU3DHOLUJAMPFA7HC37RJKB6E%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONvLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=1194acca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2FVAU3DHOLUJAMPFA7HC37RJKB6E%2F&h=6a40e63a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/VAU3DHOLUJAMPFA7HC37RJKB6E/</a>"},{"pid":"4649f8ea05f3727137327014558fc732c45c8995","tid":2177526,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T19:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82ae5e4223abfe17f1647081a9282e406d45786","tid":2177526,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4649f8ea05f3727137327014558fc732c45c8995","tid":2177526,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T19:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T19:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ebe5aa835eb3b326709beb4da60a59d35785c8","tid":2177526,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T19:29:17.000Z","msg":"洞見焯知"},{"pid":"c5407564258c30c8dedadd656fa1e91233801e5a","tid":2177526,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9ebe5aa835eb3b326709beb4da60a59d35785c8","tid":2177526,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T19:29:17.000Z","msg":"洞見焯知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T19:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}